question: Where is Odessa located in Ukraine?
true_answer: On the northwestern coast of the Black Sea.
answer: Odesa nėra Ukrainoje; ji yra svarbus jūros uostas pietų Ukrainoje, prie Juodosios jūros.
answer_translated_eng: Odessa is not in Ukraine; it is an important seaport in southern Ukraine on the Black Sea.
